{
  "page": "Unbowed, Unbent, Unbroken",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(248, 233, 208);border:none;\">\"Unbowed, Unbent, Unbroken\"</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size: 100%\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\">\n<tbody><tr style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<td style=\"width:50%;text-align:right;\">Season 5</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">&#160;—&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:50%;text-align:left;\">Episode 6</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Original air date</th><td>\nMay 17, 2015</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Running time</th><td>\n54 minutes</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">Credits</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Directed by</th><td class=\"plainlist\">\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeremy_Podeswa\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Jeremy Podeswa\">Jeremy Podeswa</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Written by</th><td class=\"plainlist\">\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bryan_Cogman\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Bryan Cogman\">Bryan Cogman</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">Episode chronology</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\">\n<tbody><tr style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<th style=\"width:50%;text-align:center;\">←&#160;Previous</th>\n<th style=\"width:50%;text-align:center;\">Next&#160;→</th>\n</tr><tr style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\"<a href=\"/index.php/Kill_the_Boy\" title=\"Kill the Boy\">Kill the Boy</a>\"</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\"<a href=\"/index.php/The_Gift\" title=\"The Gift\">The Gift</a>\"</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/List_of_Game_of_Thrones_episodes\" title=\"List of Game of Thrones episodes\">List of episodes</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>\"<b>Unbowed, Unbent, Unbroken</b>\" is the sixth episode of the <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_5\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 5\">fifth season</a> of HBO's fantasy television series <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>, and the 46th overall. The episode was written by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bryan_Cogman\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Bryan Cogman\">Bryan Cogman</a> and directed by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeremy_Podeswa\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Jeremy Podeswa\">Jeremy Podeswa</a>. It first aired on May 17th, 2015.\n</p><p>The title of the episode is the motto of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Official_synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Official synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Plot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Plot</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Production\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Production</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Writing\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Writing</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Regular_cast_members\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Regular cast members</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Guest_cast\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Guest cast</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Official_synopsis\">Official synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Unbowed,_Unbent,_Unbroken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Official synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Arya trains. Jorah and Tyrion run into slavers. Trystane and Myrcella make plans. Jaime and Bronn reach their destination.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Plot\">Plot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Unbowed,_Unbent,_Unbroken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Plot\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a> is put to the test. <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah</a> are captured by slavers. <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a> is judged by the <a href=\"/index.php/Sparrows\" title=\"Sparrows\">Sparrows</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Bronn\" title=\"Bronn\">Bronn</a> face the <a href=\"/index.php/Sand_Snakes\" title=\"Sand Snakes\">Sand Snakes</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a> marries <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Bolton\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ramsay Bolton\">Ramsay Bolton</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Production\">Production</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Unbowed,_Unbent,_Unbroken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Production\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Writing\">Writing</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Unbowed,_Unbent,_Unbroken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Writing\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>\"Unbowed, Unbent, Unbroken\" was written by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bryan_Cogman\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Bryan Cogman\">Bryan Cogman</a>, based on the original series by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a>.\n</p><p>The episode is adapted from the following chapters from the <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> series: <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_2\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 2\">The Captain of Guards</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_21\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 21\">The Queenmaker</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_22\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 22\">Arya II</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_34\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 34\">Cat of the Canals</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_39\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 39\">Cersei IX</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_41\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 41\">Alayne II</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_43\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 43\">Cersei X</a> from <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, and <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_37\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 37\">The Prince of Winterfell</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_38\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 38\">The Watcher</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_40\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 40\">Tyrion IX</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_47\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 47\">Tyrion X</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_64\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 64\">The Ugly Little Girls</a> from <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Regular_cast_members\">Regular cast members</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Unbowed,_Unbent,_Unbroken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Regular cast members\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Dinklage\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Peter Dinklage\">Peter Dinklage</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nikolaj_Coster-Waldau\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Nikolaj Coster-Waldau\">Nikolaj Coster-Waldau</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lena_Headey\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Lena Headey\">Lena Headey</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aiden_Gillen\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Aiden Gillen\">Aidan Gillen</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natalie_Dormer\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Natalie Dormer\">Natalie Dormer</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indira_Varma\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Indira Varma\">Indira Varma</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Ellaria_Sand\" title=\"Ellaria Sand\">Ellaria Sand</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maisie_Williams\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Maisie Williams\">Maisie Williams</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sophie_Turner\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Sophie Turner\">Sophie Turner</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jerome_Flynn\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Jerome Flynn\">Jerome Flynn</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Bronn\" title=\"Bronn\">Bronn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alfie_Allen\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Alfie Allen\">Alfie Allen</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Reek</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_McElhatton\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Michael McElhatton\">Michael McElhatton</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iwan_Rheon\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Iwan Rheon\">Iwan Rheon</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Bolton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_Wlaschiha\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Tom Wlaschiha\">Tom Wlaschiha</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Jaqen_H%27ghar\" title=\"Jaqen H&#39;ghar\">Jaqen H'ghar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dean-Charles_Chapman\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Dean-Charles Chapman\">Dean-Charles Chapman</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Tommen_Baratheon\" title=\"Tommen Baratheon\">Tommen I Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iain_Glen\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Iain Glen\">Iain Glen</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<p>Seventeen out of twenty-seven members for the fifth season appeared in this episode. \n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Bradley\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:John Bradley\">John Bradley</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a>), <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emilia_Clarke\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Emilia Clarke\">Emilia Clarke</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>), <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gwendoline_Christie\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Gwendoline Christie\">Gwendoline Christie</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_Tarth\" title=\"Brienne Tarth\">Brienne</a>), <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liam_Cunningham\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Liam Cunningham\">Liam Cunningham</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a>), <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_Dillane\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Stephen Dillane\">Stephen Dillane</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>), <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nathalie_Emmanuel\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Nathalie Emmanuel\">Nathalie Emmanual</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Missandei\" title=\"Missandei\">Missandei</a>), <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kit_Harington\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Kit Harington\">Kit Harington</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a>), <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conleth_Hill\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Conleth Hill\">Conleth Hill</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a>), <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carice_van_Houten\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Carice van Houten\">Carice van Houten</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a>), <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michiel_Huisman\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Michiel Huisman\">Michiel Huisman</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Daario_Naharis\" title=\"Daario Naharis\">Daario Naharis</a>), <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hannah_Murray\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Hannah Murray\">Hannah Murray</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Gilly\" title=\"Gilly\">Gilly</a>) and <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kristofer_Hivju\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Kristofer Hivju\">Kristofer Hivju</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Tormund\" title=\"Tormund\">Tormund</a>) are not credited and do not appear in this episode.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Guest_cast\">Guest cast</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Unbowed,_Unbent,_Unbroken&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Guest cast\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diana_Rigg\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Diana Rigg\">Diana Rig</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Olenna_Tyrell\" title=\"Olenna Tyrell\">Olenna Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jonathan_Pryce\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Jonathan Pryce\">Jonathan Pryce</a> as the <a href=\"/index.php/High_Sparrow\" title=\"High Sparrow\">High Sparrow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alexander_Siddig\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Alexander Siddig\">Alexander Siddig</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">Doran Martell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deobia_Oparei\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Deobia Oparei\">Deobia Oparei</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Areo_Hotah\" title=\"Areo Hotah\">Areo Hotah</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keisha_Castle-Hughes\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Keisha Castle-Hughes\">Keisha Castle-Hughes</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Obara_Sand\" title=\"Obara Sand\">Obara Sand</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rosabell_Laurenti_Sellers\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Rosabell Laurenti Sellers\">Rosabell Laurenti Sellers</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Tyene_Sand\" title=\"Tyene Sand\">Tyene Sand</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jessica_Henwick\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Jessica Henwick\">Jessica Henwick</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria_Sand\" title=\"Nymeria Sand\">Nymeria Sand</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Finn_Jones\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Finn Jones\">Finn Jones</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Will_Tudor\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Will Tudor\">Will Tudor</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Olyvar\" title=\"Olyvar\">Olyvar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eugene_Simon\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Eugene Simon\">Eugene Simon</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Lancel_Lannister\" title=\"Lancel Lannister\">Lancel Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Faye_Marsay\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Faye M